com.f2prateek.ln
Interface LnInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
DebugLn, EmptyLn, LnFacade
public interface LnInterface

LnInterface that Ln talks to. Implement this interface to provide your own endpoints, and then call Ln.set(LnInterface) with an instance of your endpoint. To post to multiple endpoints, create instances of your implementations of LnInterface, add them to LnFacade and call Ln.set(LnInterface) with an an instance of LnFacade.

getLoggingLevel

int getLoggingLevel()
Get the current logging level. Should return one of : 1. Log.VERBOSE 2. Log.ERROR 3. Log.INFO 4. Log.WARN 5. Log.ERROR 6. Log.ASSERT 7. -1 if not supported

setLoggingLevel

void setLoggingLevel(int level)
Set the logging level. Should be one of : 1. Log.VERBOSE 2. Log.ERROR 3. Log.INFO 4. Log.WARN 5. Log.ERROR 6. Log.ASSERT
